{"tid":334954,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"到底啲肥婆叫少甜係咩心態？","createTime":"2017-07-25T07:58:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-26T07:24:49.000Z","uid":33880,"like":459,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e9204d59565c9a76c235a7661c99249cc209bc93","tid":334954,"uid":33880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T07:58:21.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟就做緊間大型連鎖茶記，今日就有個肥婆入嚟食嘢。<br />\n<br />\n一個人已經有一張卡位咁闊，真係好恐怖。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於當時樓面得我一個，啲人唔知死哂去邊，我唯有頂硬上幫佢落單。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nB餐，多士要加煉奶，要多啲奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，凍檸茶少甜。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係佢講少甜個一刻，我真係忍唔住笑咗出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，唯有扮咳忍笑。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到底肥婆叫少甜係咩心態，同人講自己食得好健康？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"237de07ea316fcea50a279918c8f71251ca9c1c5","tid":334954,"uid":33880,"like":11,"dislike":6,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T08:00:45.000Z","msg":"邊個肥婆負皮我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f85593e6f63d0e210bee0178f31fcec6f0a7458b","tid":334954,"uid":119783,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T08:01:09.000Z","msg":"好撚仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48988f06e951a15d184d429c0b7d0bda6eadb527","tid":334954,"uid":3441,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T08:01:55.000Z","msg":"就係肥婆飲diet coke的心態"},{"pid":"baeead7bbea546fb4afc5da4730b7d47f3036f5b","tid":334954,"uid":39720,"like":32,"dislike":79,"score":-47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T08:02:26.000Z","msg":"純粹唔鐘意食咁甜得唔得？食甜野係致肥嘅唯一原因？"},{"pid":"4d8a0008866b0881469598ef512207954b52c9d8","tid":334954,"uid":33880,"like":30,"dislik