<br />\n一個人已經有一張卡位咁闊，真係好恐怖。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於當時樓面得我一個，啲人唔知死哂去邊，我唯有頂硬上幫佢落單。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nB餐，多士要加煉奶，要多啲奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，凍檸茶少甜。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係佢講少甜個一刻，我真係忍唔住笑咗出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，唯有扮咳忍笑。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到底肥婆叫少甜係咩心態，同人講自己食得好健康？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你笑我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n走啦肥婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2416cb8e65e7fcd9e618e1b33242fec32c8cb045","tid":334954,"uid":1403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T09:11:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我飲咩都叫少甜....有d水吧沖到杯野糖水咁...</blockquote><br />\n以前暑假返pt時老細係咁屌個水吧落得少糖水（有色果啲）搞到唔夠色水，但我試飲一啖係甜到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時唔叫少甜真係好快糖尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8967b07332e90b6784f044b55edbf46ee9806eb","tid":334954,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T09:12:03.000Z","msg":"sorry 囉，下次唔叫少甜囉"},{"pid":"bc2e6b7bab130596ea5c07d823ede556f8e26dc9","tid":334954,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T09:16:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>純粹唔鐘意食咁甜得唔得？食甜野係致肥嘅唯一原因？</blockquote><br />\n多鍊奶同時唔鍾意食甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e757aaad8b53a4b65cef7658b69d6f661c8f721f","tid":334954,"uid":129829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-2